1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO CLARIFY THE POWERS OF THE STATE AUDITOR, TO MAKE OTHER
3 CHANGES RELATED TO THE STATE AUDITOR, AND TO ALLOW THE
4 DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE TO FORCE COLLECT DEBTS OWED TO STATE
5 AGENCIES THROUGH LEVY AND SALE AND ATTACHMENT AND
6 GARNISHMENT.
