43 "§ 105A-3. Remedy Remedies additional; mandatory State usage; optional local usage;
44 usage of setoff collection only; obtaining identifying information; registration.
45 (a) Remedy Remedies Additional. – The collection remedy remedies under this Chapter
46 is are in addition to and not in substitution for any other remedy available by law.
47 …
48 (b1) Optional Local Usage. Usage of Setoff Collection Only. – A local agency may submit
49 a debt owed to it for setoff collection under this Chapter. A local agency may not submit a debt
50 owed to it for forced collection under this Chapter. A local agency that decides to submit a setoff
