8 "§ 105A-4. Minimum debt and refund.refund for setoff collection; minimum debt for
9 forced collection.
10 This Chapter applies only to (i) a setoff collection debt that is at least fifty dollars ($50.00)
11 and to a refund that is at least this same amount.amount and (ii) a forced collection debt for which
