34 PART IV. EFFECTIVE DATE
35 SECTION 13. Sections 1, 2, and 3 of this act become effective July 1, 2025, and
36 apply to contracts entered into or renewed on or after that date. G.S. 147-64.6(c)(21), as amended
37 by Section 10 of this act, becomes effective December 1, 2025. Unless otherwise provided, the
38 remainder of this act is effective when it becomes law.
